  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ClassUtil  
    JUDDIApiService
    This call is for client side access to the JUDDI API, a web service meant for administrative functions above and beyond the UDDI v3 specification.
    Release
    The release class is a utility for obtaining the version number
    UDDIService
    The UDDIService is defined by the UDDI v3 specification as the Service from which all UDDI Ports can be obtained.
    UDDIServiceV2
    The UDDIService is defined by the UDDI v2 specification as the Service from which all UDDI Ports can be obtained.
    UDDIv2Constants
    UDDI v2 Constants, such as supported find qualifiers.
